name: ゆきめ - Yukime LORA. / Jigoku Sensei Nūbē - 地獄先生ぬ～べ～
description:
28th Release, ゆきめ - Yukime From Jigoku Sensei Nūbē - 地獄先生ぬ～べ～.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

Character's request from my Poll, i Tryed to be the Most precise with the Best Quality Possible for Yukime.

About this Lora:

  • Lora trained on 84+ Images that i sorted manually, at the max quality possible (Original Art + Official Anime Art, Were used in the datasets) SFW+.

  • Can do Official Skin Precisely. (Also can do Yukime in Recent & 1990s Anime Style).

  • Flexibility is Very Good, Very Flexible.

  • Trained at 512x Resolution.

  • NAI Used, Work with Majority of the Anime Model's.

  • Work's Perfectly at Weight 1. (1.1,1.2).

  • Work's greatly with 1990s Anime Style Lora, Or Retro 1990s prompts.

For Prompts & Weight:

Flexibility is Very Good. (See examples images).

About Trigger Words & Prompts: YukimeV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples images.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Best Result 0.8-1.1.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

modelVersions.name: V4
modelVersions.description:
I pruned Blue Hair, Blue Eyes, Long Sidelocks so normally you don't need to put in prompt, but if they don't appear put: ((Blue Hair, Blue Eyes, Long Sidelocks)) prompt.

For Official Default Skin: Work perfectly at Weight 1, (1.1-1.2). You can also do 1990s Anime Style with a Lora or Prompts.

For Flexibility: for like clothes that don't exist put 0.6 - 1 Weight, See my Examples images for this.
